@@TJvCustomLabel.HotTrack
Summary
  Specifies whether the label is highlighted when the mouse passes over it.
Description
  Set HotTrack to true to provide visual feedback about which item is under the mouse; the font
  specified by HotTrackFont is used for the label text. When HotTrack is false, there is no visual
  feedback when the mouse passes over the label.

